Class AddNewMomentsPage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pom.crimson.base.BaseFixture

        • com.pom.crimson.pages.AddNewMomentsPage
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EditMomentPage

    public class AddNewMomentsPage
extends BasePage
    AddNewMomentsPage or New moment page can be used to add moments for primary profile or child profiles.
    User can navigate to this page by going to:

    Go to Home Page
    Click "Moments log" widget
    Click "Add new moment" link

    This page class contains MobileElements on this page and functions to simulate interactions with these elements.
    Author:
    Jaspreet Kaur Chagger

      • createMomentWithMilestone

        public MomentsLogPage createMomentWithMilestone(java.lang.String milestone,
                                                java.lang.String profileName)
        Create a moment with Recommended milestones only.
        Recommended milestones are shown in Whose moment is it? section as per tab selected Myself or preferred name of related child tab
        If a Archetype selected in Profile is Parent to be than pregnancy milestones will be displayed in Myself tab as per Due date.
        If a related Child profile is added in Profile section than Recommended milestones will be displayed in preferred name of related child tab as per child's date of birth.
        Parameters:
        milestone - Recommended milestone name
        profileName - tab to selected in Whose moment is it? section. (Values: Myself or preferred name of related child)
        Returns:
        Object of MomentsLogPage
